Capital Markets

Company Overview of Nomura International plc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nomura International plc, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a securities broker/dealer in the United Kingdom. The company trades in and sells fixed income and equity products, including related derivatives; and provides investment banking services, and corporate finance and private equity services. It is also involved in asset and principal finance business. In addition, the company offers investment advisory and management, employment, custody, and corporate trustee services. The company was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in London, United Kingdom. Nomura International plc operates as a subsidiary of Nomura Europe Holdings plc.


1 Angel LaneLondon,  EC4R 3ABUnited KingdomFounded in 19812,635 Employees



