   Nomura International is the UK-based subsidiary of Japan's Nomura Holdings. The company provides securities brokering, dealing, investment banking and advisory, corporate finance, asset management and custody services for individual, institutional, corporate, and government customers. The firm trades fixed income and equity products, including related derivatives. It also provides employment services, and makes private equity investments in technology and life sciences firms. Nomura International is based in London, but also operates in about a dozen other European and Middle Eastern countries.
  







